item.title: MEET the blogger
item.description: MEET the blogger Paving the roads with good intentions Some call me “Carl.” I am the blogger behind the keys. I am a semi-retired teacher of language arts and a small business owner, a husband, a stepdad, and an uncle extraordinaire, a chef, a writer, a packer of gift boxes, a deliverer of parcels, and a former managing editor of Texas’ oldest weekly publication. I rather enjoy creative ventures and learning new things.
